flowchart TB
    U[客户端/上游服务] --> APP[Go 应用集群\n有界并发/幂等/熔断]
    APP -->|rw-db.service:6432| PB1[PgBouncer A]
    APP -->|rw-db.service:6432| PB2[PgBouncer B]
    PB1 --> VIP[HAProxy 双实例/VIP 或云 LB]
    PB2 --> VIP

    subgraph AZA[AZ-A]
      PGA[pg-a\nPatroni + PostgreSQL\n当前 Primary]
      E1[etcd-1]
    end
    subgraph AZB[AZ-B]
      PGB[pg-b\nPatroni + PostgreSQL\n当前 Sync Replica]
      E2[etcd-2]
    end
    subgraph AZC[AZ-C]
      PGC[pg-c\nPatroni + PostgreSQL\n当前 Async/候选 Replica]
      E3[etcd-3]
    end

    VIP -->|/primary 健康检查后转发 SQL| PGA
    VIP -.候选.-> PGB
    VIP -.候选.-> PGC

    PGA ==>|WAL streaming + sync ack| PGB
    PGA -->|WAL streaming| PGC

    PGA <-->|Leader Lock/成员/同步状态| E1
    PGA <-->|DCS quorum| E2
    PGA <-->|DCS quorum| E3
    PGB <-->|DCS| E1
    PGB <-->|DCS| E2
    PGB <-->|DCS| E3
    PGC <-->|DCS| E1
    PGC <-->|DCS| E2
    PGC <-->|DCS| E3

    PGA -->|WAL archive| REPO[异区域 pgBackRest Repository\n不可变存储/保留策略]
    PGB -.restore/backup.-> REPO
    PGC -.restore/backup.-> REPO

    MON[Prometheus/Grafana/日志/告警] --> PGA
    MON --> PGB
    MON --> PGC
    MON --> E1
    MON --> E2
    MON --> E3
    MON --> PB1
    MON --> VIP

    ADM[受控管理入口\nMFA + 审批 + 审计] --> CTL[patronictl/etcdctl/pgBackRest]
    CTL --> PGA
    CTL --> E1
    CTL --> REPO

    PGA -.异步 WAL/归档.-> DR[跨区域 Standby Cluster\n独立 DCS/独立入口]
